snippet.title: acai cOrner - Spooky RPG Maker 2003 dungeon crawling!
snippet.description:
"Your name is Mizuki. You have fallen into the sewers. You find your favorite guitar! You feel different. You are a magical girl now. There are monsters everywhere. It gets harder to breathe the further you go... Short Surreal adventure-spooky game!"

Download the game here: https://rpgmaker.net/games/11377/
